parameters: \N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe...

\N<Princess Consort Suia>Stop right there, Zuuteruka! I will not allow you to come
any closer!
\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, is that so? And what happens if I do come closer?
\N<Princess Consort Suia>Are you... out of your mind!?

\N<Zuuteruka>Of course I am. If I weren't crazy, I wouldn't be able to do
something so audacious. Or do your beautiful eyes see me as
a madman?

\N<Princess Consort Suia>Nonsense...! Zuuteruka, you are the very picture of a madman
right now, aren't you!?

\N<Princess Consort Suia>Taking over the vigilante squad, coordinating with the
outsiders of Luda, and inviting enemy soldiers into the
castle... These are not the actions of a sane person! If
this isn't madness, then what is it!?
\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, that's some harsh criticism.

\N<Princess Consort Suia>What... what is your goal!? I can't believe you would scheme
such things without reason!

\N<Princess Consort Suia>What is your objective!? What are you planning by conspiring
with Luda!?
\N<Zuuteruka>Objective, huh... Well now, what could it be?
\N<Princess Consort Suia>What did you say...!?

\N<Zuuteruka>I don't know what those guys from Luda who teamed up with
me are after. But my objective is crystal clear.

\N<Zuuteruka>But even if you knew it now, it wouldn't mean anything to
you. Instead of worrying about that, you should be more
concerned about your own safety.
\N<Princess Consort Suia>Gah...!

\N<Princess Consort Suia>My husband... What has happened to His Grace the Archduke!?
Answer me!

\N<Zuuteruka>Those Luda folks are no better than bloodthirsty beasts.
They're only interested in things and money that benefit
them, and women, nothing else.

\N<Zuuteruka>What about His Grace the Archduke? Is he someone who would
be of benefit to them? Hehehe... Well, by now his head might
have parted ways with his body?
\N<Princess Consort Suia>You... you monster...!!

\N<Princess Consort Suia>Listen well and remember this! If you dare lay a hand on my
husband or Yuia, I will never forgive you...!
\N<Zuuteruka>Oh, scary scary. Understood, I'll take it to heart.

\N<Princess Consort Suia>Is that... Is that the attitude of a guard belonging to this
castle's vigilante squad!?
\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe 'former'... right.
